---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Provenance — Essenfont" description="Glyph provenance and attribution for every codepoint in the Essenfont." canonical="/provenance">
  <article class="provenance-page">
    <header class="page-head">
      <h1>Glyph attribution</h1>
    </header>
    <section class="prose">
      <p>Every glyph in Essenfont is traceable to its donor font. The build pipeline records which donor contributed each codepoint, and this mapping is available as <code>cp_map.json</code> in each GitHub Release.</p>
      <p>The <a href="/donors">donor registry</a> lists all {38} source fonts and their license terms. For the full per-codepoint attribution, download the release and inspect <code>cp_map.json</code>.</p>
      <h2>Reproducibility</h2>
      <p>The build is fully reproducible from the committed manifest:</p>
      <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/essenfont/essenfont
cd essenfont
bundle install
FONTISAN_PATH=../fontist/fontisan bundle exec ruby scripts/build.rb --format=otc-cff2</code></pre>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
.provenance-page { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem; }
.page-head { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

h1 { font-family: var(--spec-font-display); font-size: 2rem; }
</style>
